{"tid":483871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友脫髮，求醫生或方法介紹","createTime":"2017-11-29T14:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T01:25:33.000Z","uid":50620,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"afb8db302e58d9742804f95de261a9546e1af64f","tid":483871,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"佢本來都有d甩，但近排發現佢明顯左<br />\n我本身都後移都好明甩髮種感受<br />\n尤其佢係女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係介意佢外型，只係知真心想幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n介紹少少佢背景<br />\n成日鍾意食辣，打邊爐，煎炸野<br />\n偏肥<br />\n返醫院，所以壓力都大<br />\n唔運動<br />\n因為多白髮搞到2,3個月就染一次頭<br />\n今年23歲<br />\n唔係斑禿，分界位都幾明顯<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人可以幫忙，介紹下方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086798323c5dcaf865938a6128de5754897b68bb","tid":483871,"uid":63450,"like":26,"dislike":10,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:10:21.000Z","msg":"試下換左個女朋友"},{"pid":"14c39b7e2118429d851132a4e53934ca69feeab9","tid":483871,"uid":15954,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:11:41.000Z","msg":"雄禿"},{"pid":"ab10a88b2269cc8b60ce830766ff7ebed09695e7","tid":483871,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雄禿</blockquote><br />\n有冇醫生介紹？<br />\n<br />\n聽聞女人冇得好似男人咁食藥"},{"pid":"a007d786da381e113e9d45f6968887bcc61e90a3","tid":483871,"uid":146537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雄禿</blockquote><br />\n有冇醫生介紹？<br />\n<br />\n聽聞女人冇得好似男人咁食藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生髮水<br />\nsaw palmetto 唔知女仔岩唔岩食"},{"pid":"31c8a0ecc3754b5021a4fc6fdeb012cfe28269c6","tid":483871,"uid":29070,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T14:24:03.000Z","msg":"試吓搽你啲精液"},{"pid":"71eff60cf6b2fb1b56f86179e0949cb71fd8a778","tid":483871,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"