al/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死妹釘唔食黑芝麻同好少食黑色既野補腎<br />\n<br />\n有冇乜補品幫到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己有食維特健靈，我一出黎做野就有髮線後移問題<br />\n但食左之後好似停左，依家叫高，但唔算後<br />\n個人又精神左<br />\n呢啲幾百蚊一樽食成個月<br />\n巴打我覺得你除左搵啲快嘅方法之外<br />\n呢啲慢性補野都可以試下"},{"pid":"2f71517a59b9d3ac0c862d90ca408b4c2a69b182","tid":483871,"uid":5605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"缺鐵都有機會，去做個身體檢查先啦"},{"pid":"46f8e1869654bf06cdcdb6066b57dc4bdfe3690e","tid":483871,"uid":5605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:36:50.000Z","msg":"缺鐵都有機會，去做個身體檢查先啦"},{"pid":"10d76200788cc1d4047e9ccfba4378314094f49c","tid":483871,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:38:58.000Z","msg":"可能甲狀線有問題, <br />\n不過23歲都咁,<br />\n身體都幾差下, 有排調理,"},{"pid":"06c07f182dc58ab5b466d8aee99098fb95c794e3","tid":483871,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>補下肝腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死妹釘唔食黑芝麻同好少食黑色既野補腎<br />\n<br />\n有冇乜補品幫到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx絲打<br />\n<br />\n佢會間中飲酒都應該需要"},{"pid":"fb02051bea0a966b24ee3d482d0db8a8cf50dc49","tid":483871,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T04:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>補下肝腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死妹釘唔食黑芝麻同好少食黑色既野補腎<br />\n<br />\n有冇乜補品幫到？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己有食維特健靈，我一出黎做野就有髮線後移問題<br />\n但食左之後好似停左，依家叫高，但唔算後<br />\n個人又精神左<br />\n呢啲幾百蚊一樽食成個月<br />\n巴打我覺得你除左搵啲快嘅方法之外<br />\n呢啲慢性補野都可以試下</blockquote><br />\n會丫，外內幫補睇下會唔會好d先"