<br />\n<br />\n利申：曾經都嚴重甩髮，宜家冇乜點甩過"},{"pid":"a0ef3f484c6d2d49a966176284917d5ee4a9915a","tid":483871,"uid":18952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"之前減完肥發覺d分界好明顯甩左好多頭髮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇左皮膚科醫生 比左支生髮水 但之後上網research 見好傷身就停左 開始用 LUSH 隻洗頭 soap (紅色防脫髮用) 我自己感覺係甩少左 但個分界都係未生番頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後 髮型師叫我不如剪短佢 剪短個一年真係甩得再少d 可能髮型問題 我都見個分界多番d頭髮了 <br />\n如果女友係長髮 不妨建議佢剪短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e88f32b8403a85d9e9b57d877eaf8f40b36d16","tid":483871,"uid":67315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"試下用五十惠"},{"pid":"922a557e0e7d81a01dfb2eae0d95d021d835f90b","tid":483871,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:42:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下用五十惠</blockquote><br />\n巴打請問響邊度買?<br />\n好難搵到"},{"pid":"9b528575fe3dbed71cea955d0717ad9bb3b89cc3","tid":483871,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:54:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>女人好少會咁架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少就唔會有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有有話唔會咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d50dc80c65f5655f022cb7eb1cf1b938e3975a","tid":483871,"uid":21629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>女人好少會咁架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n少就唔會有咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor